text: The Council of the Isles of Scilly is the local government for the Isles of Scilly. There are 16 councilors in it, they help run the Isles of Scilly, but don't make any laws. Only the Parliament of the United Kingdom can make laws for the Isles of Scilly. ==References== Category:Isles of Scilly Category:Government of Cornwall
title: Council of the Isles of Scilly
